<view class="container"><view class="hero-card"><view class="hero-tag">数据驱动健康中心</view><view class="hero-title">健康记录与趋势分析</view><view class="hero-grid"><view class="hero-metric"><view class="metric-label">最新体重</view><view class="metric-value">{{latestRecord?latestRecord.weight:'--'}}</view><view class="metric-unit">kg</view></view><view class="hero-metric"><view class="metric-label">最新 BMI</view><view class="metric-value">{{latestRecord?latestRecord.bmi:'--'}}</view><view class="metric-unit">指数</view></view><view class="hero-metric"><view class="metric-label">近7天记录</view><view class="metric-value">{{recentCount}}</view><view class="metric-unit">条</view></view></view></view><view class="two-col"><view class="section-card half"><view class="section-title">体型目标进度</view><view class="kv-row"><text>当前体重</text><text>{{(currentWeightForProgress||'--')+" kg"}}</text></view><view class="kv-row"><text>目标体重</text><text>{{(profile.target_weight||'--')+" kg"}}</text></view><view class="kv-row"><text>达成度</text><text>{{goalProgress+"%"}}</text></view><view class="progress-bg"><view class="progress-bar" style="{{'width:'+(goalProgress+'%')+';'}}"></view></view><view class="tips">可以作为答辩时的“可视化反馈”展示。</view></view><view class="section-card half"><view class="section-title">一周状态摘要</view><view class="kv-row"><text>平均体重</text><text>{{weeklyAvgWeight}}</text></view><view class="kv-row"><text>平均体脂估算</text><text>{{weeklyAvgFat}}</text></view><view class="kv-row"><text>趋势变化</text><text>{{weightTrendText}}</text></view><view class="kv-row"><text>健康判断</text><text>{{healthJudge}}</text></view></view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-head"><view class="section-title">趋势图</view><view class="tab-row"><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['e0',['$event']]]]]}}" class="{{['tab',(chartMode==='weight')?'active':'']}}" bindtap="__e">体重</text><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['e1',['$event']]]]]}}" class="{{['tab',(chartMode==='body_fat')?'active':'']}}" bindtap="__e">体脂估算</text><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['e2',['$event']]]]]}}" class="{{['tab',(chartMode==='bmi')?'active':'']}}" bindtap="__e">BMI</text></view></view><block wx:if="{{$root.g0<2}}"><view class="empty-text">暂无足够数据绘制趋势图，请先添加 2 条以上健康记录。</view></block><block wx:else><view class="chart-box"><svg class="chart-svg" vue-id="179c960c-1" viewBox="0 0 690 240" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><defs vue-id="{{('179c960c-2')+','+('179c960c-1')}}" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><linear-gradient vue-id="{{('179c960c-3')+','+('179c960c-2')}}" id="lineGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><stop vue-id="{{('179c960c-4')+','+('179c960c-3')}}" offset="0%" stop-color="#4f46e5" bind:__l="__l"></stop><stop vue-id="{{('179c960c-5')+','+('179c960c-3')}}" offset="100%" stop-color="#06b6d4" bind:__l="__l"></stop></linear-gradient></defs><polyline vue-id="{{('179c960c-6')+','+('179c960c-1')}}" points="{{chartAreaPoints}}" fill="rgba(79,70,229,0.08)" stroke="none" bind:__l="__l"></polyline><polyline vue-id="{{('179c960c-7')+','+('179c960c-1')}}" points="{{chartPoints}}" fill="none" stroke="url(#lineGradient)" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" bind:__l="__l"></polyline><block wx:for="{{pointNodes}}" wx:for-item="point" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><g vue-id="{{('179c960c-8-'+index)+','+('179c960c-1')}}" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><circle vue-id="{{('179c960c-9-'+index)+','+('179c960c-8-'+index)}}" cx="{{point.x}}" cy="{{point.y}}" r="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#4f46e5" stroke-width="3" bind:__l="__l"></circle><text x="{{point.x}}" y="{{point.y-12}}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#334155">{{point.label}}</text><text x="{{point.x}}" y="228" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#94a3b8">{{point.dateLabel}}</text></g></block></svg></view></block></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">新增健康记录</view><view class="tips">除了体重，系统会自动计算 BMI、BMR 和体脂估算。</view><view class="label">体重（kg）</view><input class="input" placeholder="例如 59.5" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','weight','$event',[]],['form']]]]]}}" value="{{form.weight}}" bindinput="__e"/><view class="label">训练/状态备注</view><textarea class="textarea" placeholder="例如：今天完成快走 40 分钟，状态不错" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','note','$event',[]],['form']]]]]}}" value="{{form.note}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['submitRecord',['$event']]]]]}}" class="btn primary" bindtap="__e">保存健康记录</view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">记录时间线</view><block wx:if="{{$root.g1}}"><view><block wx:for="{{records}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="__i0__" wx:key="id"><view class="timeline-item"><view class="timeline-dot"></view><view class="timeline-content"><view class="timeline-title">{{item.record_date+" ｜ "+item.weight+" kg"}}</view><view class="timeline-desc">{{"BMI："+item.bmi+" ｜ 体脂估算："+(item.body_fat||'--')+"%"}}</view><view class="timeline-note">{{item.note||'暂无备注'}}</view></view></view></block></view></block><block wx:else><view class="empty-text">暂无健康记录</view></block></view></view>